These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, argentine
1. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the french##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Nationality   | french | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, roller
1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Transport   | scooter | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | drama |

